CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,FA convenience store has been shut down
OL,8,Fand thousands of illegal vapes seized
OL,9,Fas a secret compartment was found in
OL,10,Fthe ceiling.
OL,12,FMoreton Convenience Store in the
OL,13,FWirral has been closed for a maximum
OL,14,Fof three months- the tenth closure by
OL,15,Fthe local council since December 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,FKevin Burn, an officer within Wirral's
OL,8,FTrading Standards team, told Wirral
OL,9,FMagistrates Court a fob was found when
OL,10,Fthey issued the closure notice, and a
OL,11,F"compartment came down" with "4,500
OL,12,Fcigarettes, illegal counterfeit
OL,13,Fcigarettes".
OL,15,FAndrea Fitzgerald, prosecuting on
OL,16,Fbehalf of Wirral Council, said the
OL,17,Fcouncil's trading standards team had
OL,18,Fcarried out four enforcement visits
OL,19,Fseizing 1,760 illegal cigarettes,
OL,20,F150kg of hand-rolled tobacco, and
OL,21,F2,042 illegal vapes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,FThe Local Democracy Reporting Service
OL,8,F(LDRS) report that three test
OL,9,Fpurchases had also been carried out
OL,10,Fwhere illegal cigarettes and tobacco
OL,11,Fproducts were sold.
OL,13,FMs Fitzgerald also said they "have
OL,14,Falso had intelligence reports from
OL,15,Fpolice about the sales of vapes to
OL,16,Fminors".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,FShe said all of those involved in the
OL,8,Fbusiness were aware of the closure
OL,9,Forder and Merseyside Police supported
OL,10,Fthe action taken by the local
OL,11,Fauthority.
OL,13,FCllr Graeme Cooper, who chairs the
OL,14,Fcouncil's health committee, said:
OL,15,F"What is particularly worrying is when
OL,16,Fyou consider that it is young people
OL,17,Fwho will be more likely to purchase
OL,18,Fthese products as they are being sold
OL,19,Fcheap, unregulated and without legal
OL,20,Fchecks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,F"Any business that is selling this
OL,8,Ftype of product, they are causing a
OL,9,Fsignificant health risk to the
OL,10,Fcommunities they are operating in and
OL,11,Fthe people they sell to. These
OL,12,Factivities are a public health threat,
OL,13,Ffundamentally undermining tobacco
OL,14,Fcontrol strategies and proper,
OL,15,Feffective methods to help people stop
OL,16,Fsmoking.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,F"Residents have told us that they want
OL,8,Faction to stop these illegal and
OL,9,Fharmful tobacco products from being
OL,10,Fsold in their communities and the
OL,11,FTrading Standards team deserves praise
OL,12,Fand our thanks for their hard work in
OL,13,Ftaking down such a large-scale
OL,14,Foperation as this."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,FCllr Ann Ainsworth, vice chair of the
OL,8,Fcommittee overseeing trading
OL,9,Fstandards, said: "Our Trading
OL,10,FStandards service is absolutely
OL,11,Fcommitted to tackling anyone involved
OL,12,Fin these illegal operations, working
OL,13,Falongside the police and acting on
OL,14,Finformation and intelligence received.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,F"It is vital that we find and seize
OL,8,Fthese goods to get them off the market
OL,9,Fand ultimately bring offenders to
OL,10,Fjustice. There are clear links between
OL,11,Fthe illicit trade of cigarettes and
OL,12,Fwider organised crime and that is
OL,13,Fbefore we even consider the potential
OL,14,Fhealth risks of people using these
OL,15,Funtested and illegal products."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
