PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775401882
OL,3,CShop shut down after 'secret
OL,4,Ccompartment' found with thousands of
OL,5,Cillegal vapes
OL,7,FThe council said the case was the 10th
OL,8,Ftime they had pursued a closure order
OL,9,Fagainst a premises. A spokesperson
OL,10,Fsaid: "More closure orders in respect
OL,11,Fof other premises within the borough
OL,12,Fare in the process of being prepared."
OL,14,FAnyone with information or
OL,15,Fintelligence about illegal activity is
OL,16,Fbeing urged report it anonymously to
OL,17,FCrimestoppers on 0800 555 111.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
